patthana11.15:1.1: Nasavitakkasavicāraṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naavitakkavicāramattaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naavitakkaavicāraṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:2.1: Hetuyā aṭṭhacattālīsa, ārammaṇe sattacattālīsa …pe… purejāte āsevane chacattālīsa …pe… avigate aṭṭhacattālīsa.
patthana11.15:3.1: Napītisahagataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nasukhasahagataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naupekkhāsahagataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:4.1: Hetuyā ekūnapaññāsa …pe… purejāte āsevane aṭṭhacattālīsa …pe… avigate ekūnapaññāsa.
patthana11.15:5.1: Nadassanena pahātabbaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabhāvanāya pahātabbaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevadassanena nabhāvanāya pahātabbaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:6.1: Hetuyā ekūnatiṁsa, ārammaṇe catuvīsa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekūnatiṁsa.
patthana11.15:7.1: Nadassanena pahātabbahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevadassanena nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:8.1: Hetuyā ekūnatiṁsa, ārammaṇe catuvīsa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekūnatiṁsa.
patthana11.15:9.1: Naācayagāmiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naapacayagāmiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevācayagāmināpacayagāmiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:10.1: Hetuyā ekavīsa, ārammaṇe sattarasa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekavīsa.
patthana11.15:11.1: Nasekkhaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naasekkhaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevāsekkhanāsekkhaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:12.1: Hetuyā ekūnatiṁsa, ārammaṇe catuvīsa …pe… āsevane nava …pe… avigate ekūnatiṁsa.
patthana11.15:13.1: Naparittaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namahaggataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naappamāṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:14.1: Hetuyā bāttiṁsa, ārammaṇe sattavīsa …pe… aññamaññe tiṁsa …pe… avigate bāttiṁsa.
patthana11.15:15.1: Naparittārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namahaggatārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naappamāṇārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha ekūnapaññāsa.)
patthana11.15:16.1: Nahīnaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namajjhimaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… napaṇītaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:17.1: Hetuyā ekūnatiṁsa, ārammaṇe catuvīsa …pe… āsevane sattarasa, vipāke ekavīsa …pe… avigate ekūnatiṁsa.
patthana11.15:18.1: Namicchattaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nasammattaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:19.1: Hetuyā ekavīsa, ārammaṇe sattarasa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekavīsa.
patthana11.15:20.1: Namaggārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namaggahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namaggādhipatiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha ekūnapaññāsa.)
patthana11.15:21.1: Naanuppannaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nauppādiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava.)
patthana11.15:22.1: Naatītaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naanāgataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava.)
patthana11.15:23.1: Naatītārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naanāgatārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… napaccuppannārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha ekūnapaññāsa.)
patthana11.15:24.1: Naajjhattaṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabahiddhā nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha dve.)
patthana11.15:25.1: Naajjhattārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabahiddhārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava.)
